column2: SELECT    m.name as name, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,    m.objid AS HSC_objid,       m.gmag_psf     AS HSC_gmag_psf,   m.gmag_psf_err AS HSC_gmag_psf_err,      m.rmag_psf     AS HSC_rmag_psf,   m.rmag_psf_err AS HSC_rmag_psf_err,      m.imag_psf     AS HSC_imag_psf,   m.imag_psf_err AS HSC_imag_psf_err,      m.zmag_psf     AS HSC_zmag_psf,   m.zmag_psf_err AS HSC_zmag_psf_err,      m.ymag_psf     AS HSC_ymag_psf,   m.ymag_psf_err AS HSC_ymag_psf_err,         n.objID, n.distance,      p.ra AS ra2, p.dec AS dec2,           p.psfMag_g, p.psfMagErr_g,       p.psfMag_r, p.psfMagErr_r,       p.psfMag_i, p.psfMagErr_i,       p.psfMag_z, p.psfMagErr_z,          p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r,       p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z    into HSC_star_DR1#    FROM MyDB.HSC_sql_query_star_ra_dec  AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON n.objID = p.objID
